snippet.title: Destiny 2: Lightfall Trailer | The Game Awards 2022
snippet.description:
Cancel the apocalypse with the latest chapter in Destiny 2 with Lightfall.  Bungie gave us a closer look at the neon soaked world of the forthcoming expansion coming February 28, 2023. 

#Destiny2 #Lightfall #Destiny #Bungie
